text: How Many Development Feeds Can you Follow?
To all of you information addicts out there - I was wondering how much information can you take.
At the moment I have 104 active subscriptions on my google reader, mostly development stuff, and I can barely keep up.
I do not really read all the stuff that gets posted - I scan with my eyes and if my fast forward algorithm gets some keyword I am interested in I go back and read.
How many Development feeds can you follow (assuming you get your day-job done)?
